OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with some good
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine. However, skies
OL,7,Fwill cloud over through the morning,
OL,8,Fperhaps with a few showers for a time.
OL,9,FWarm bright spells developing again in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClouding over again this
OL,13,Fevening with a few light showers
OL,14,Fpossible overnight. Staying mild under
OL,15,Fthe blanket of cloud with light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FTurning increasingly bright
OL,18,Fin the morning with some good spells
OL,19,Fof sunshine. Heavier rain then likely
OL,20,Fto arrive during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
