OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fdrier picture over the next few days
OL,7,Fwith some warm spells of sunshine.
OL,8,FSunshine will be hazy at times and it
OL,9,Fwill feel increasingly humid.
